                                                  <quote rend="blockquote">
                                                                 <l> οὐδ᾽ εἷλὲ πώ <note resp="ed" place="unspecified" anchored="yes"><foreign lang="greek">πώ</foreign>] <foreign lang="greek">κώ</foreign> σξηνειδεωινυς</note> με ζῆλος, οὐδ᾽ ἀγαίομαι </l> <note resp="ed" place="unspecified" anchored="yes">βεργκ. 2 π. 390</note>
